-- ===================== Stored Procedures (sp*) =====================

-- SKIPPED: spCreateAIAgent has 101 parameters, exceeding PostgreSQL's
-- hard limit of 100 function arguments (FUNC_MAX_ARGS). The canonical PG-side
-- representation for wide CRUD sprocs is the JSON-arg shape
-- (CREATE FUNCTION spCreateAIAgent(p_data JSONB)). CodeGen emits that form via
-- V202605071645__v5.33.x__Force_Regen_All_CRUD_Sprocs_JSON_Arg_Shape and
